<info gid="1381155417" type="Plot Summary">The story takes place in a trading city Ert'Aria. Leicester Maycraft is an item engineer belonging to an adventurer guild &quot;Oasis&quot;. One night, he is at a party with his friends to see a meteor stream on the rooftop of a chapel. One meteor grazes them and hits the steeple of the chapel. There he finds a secret room and a sleeping girl. The girl wakes up and says &quot;You must be my father&quot;. The encounter with the mysterious girl brings an unexpected adventure to Leicester.</info>
